00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,000
Yeah, Bill.

136
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,000
Do you have a plot?

137
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,000
Yeah, I thought you had one.

138
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,000
Okay.

139
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,000
He'll show that.

