00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:38,000
Do you have a processing schedule yet?

157
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:40,000
I, I guess it's all in advance to figure out what to do next.

158
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:44,000
Yeah, everything is on a hold until this afternoon, yeah, after we're meeting this afternoon.

159
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:48,000
Assuming you're determined to go ahead and develop it, will it take you three or four days

